name: Velo Kitty
description:
Velo Kitty is a fish delivery feline on a remote cat island in Japan.
Deliver 10 fish to the island's restaurant as fast as you can!
But watch out for other hungry cats, they're out to steal your fishy parcels.

Controls:

  • Left/Right Arrows: Move
  • Down Arrow: Brakes
  • Space: Jump
  • Escape: Restart/Quit

Credits:

  • Art: Iris Wong (@demonography) & Kate Prescesky (@kateprescesky)
  • Design/Development: Justin Luk (@madcapacity)
  • Music: Kyle Reczek (@savethejets)
  • Sfx: ChipTone (http://sfbgames.com/chiptone/)
